  "title": "Old age mortality in Eastern and South-Eastern Asia",
  "abstract": "Eastern and South-Eastern Asian countries have witnessed a marked decline in old age mortality in recent decades. Yet no studies have investigated the trends and patterns in old age mortality and cause-of-death in the region.",
